comments: Hield (SAC) and Clark (NOP) engage and disengage off ball.
Bagley III (SAC) makes marginal contact to Wood's (NOP) body during his shooting motion that does not affect his play at the basket.
Payton (NOP) makes marginal contact to Fox's (SAC) body during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Hield (SAC) makes marginal arm to arm contact with Clark (NOP) off ball.
Cauley-Stein (SAC) establishes himself in a picking position in the path of Payton (NOP) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Wood (NOP) makes incidental contact to Bagley III's (SAC) wrist after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Randle (NOP) makes contact with the ball and simultaneously makes incidental contact with Hield's (SAC) arm during rebounding.
RAR shows Fox (SAC) makes marginal contact to Payton's (NOP) body during his shooting motion on his driving shot attempt.
Bagley III (SAC) and Payton (NOP) make incidental contact with one another during the rebound.
Clark (NOP) and Hield (SAC) engage and disengage off ball.
Williams (NOP) makes marginal contact with Barnes (SAC) off ball that does not affect his ability to get to the pass.
LLS shows Williams (NOP) makes incidental contact with Barnes's (SAC) off arm during his upward shooting motion on his jump shot attempt.
Hield (SAC) places a forearm to Randle's (NOP) front during the drive but the contact is marginal.
Fox (SAC) makes marginal body contact with Randle (NOP) and avoids making contact with his head.
Payton (NOP) engages with Fox (SAC) during the inbound but does not prevent him from setting the screen.
[Observable in enhanced video] Hield (SAC) lifts his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Fox (SAC) commits a take foul on Wood (NOP).
